{"tid":1945411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地香港需唔需要梁美芬？","createTime":"2020-03-27T04:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T04:41:44.000Z","uid":229185,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3992734029be6d753f9cbaea85ca69c04322ceca","tid":1945411,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5egpBdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5egpBdj.jpg&h=11149b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/453061/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%BC%A0%E6%82%A3%E6%9C%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%88%90%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%86%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BF%99%E6%96%BC%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%A1%A7%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%B1%E5%BD%BC?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F453061%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E6%2582%25A3%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%259A%25B1%25E6%2586%2582-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2586%2582%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25BF%2599%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25BD%25BC%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNpIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=4538a314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/453061/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%BC%A0%E6%82%A3%E6%9C%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%88%90%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%86%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BF%99%E6%96%BC%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%A1%A7%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%B1%E5%BD%BC?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news</a><br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉在即，由經民聯梁美芬率領「西九新動力」打出「滅鼠牌」，今日宣布新成立組織「撲滅鼠患大聯盟」。梁美芬會上稱，「香港應該區區都出有一個鼠王芬」，監察食環署的滅鼠工作。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬稱，自己雖然是教法律，「但我從政以來，多了個綽號，多得大家賜畀我，就是『鼠王芬』。」梁美芬指出，「鼠王芬」平日被醜化，「平時大家笑下，或者譏笑，唔鍾意的人用來取笑，負面醜化。」她稱，「今日要講，應該區區都有一個鼠王芬，努力鞭策食環署，唔好自己高高在上，做議員、做政府官員唔該落社區睇下。」<br />\n成立撲鼠大聯盟　梁美芬：香港應該區區都出一個「鼠王芬」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%92%B2%E9%BC%A0%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E9%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B-%E9%BC%A0%E7%8E%8B%E8%8A%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2592%25B2%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258A%25AC-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B-%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%258A%25AC%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNpIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=4b83ee63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2592%25B2%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258A%25AC-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B-%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%258A%25AC%2F&h=12adae74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%92%B2%E9%BC%A0%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E9%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B-%E9%BC%A0%E7%8E%8B%E8%8A%AC/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔需要，仇B 可以做鼠王<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要， 鼠王芬永遠係鼠王芬"},{"pid":"4c0f8a063be91aeeaee2a1ef1cf636412979eb0c","